OL,5, Prime Minister Rishi Sunak has         
OL,6, criticised changes to Roald Dahl books,
OL,7, after the removal of some references to
OL,8, things like characters' appearance and 
OL,9, weight sparked a fierce debate.        
OL,11,FDahl's estate and publisher said works 
OL,12,Fincluding The BFG and Charlie and the  
OL,13,FChocolate Factory had been updated to  
OL,14,Fbe more suitable for modern audiences. 
OL,16,FSome said they approved of the changes.
OL,18,FBut Mr Sunak's spokesman said works of 
OL,19,Ffiction should be "preserved and not   
OL,20,Fairbrushed".                           
